 and we=E2=80=99re going to try to make sure that=E2=80=99s not the case go=
ing forward=E2=80=9D.*

*NF:* Yeah, I think Satya knows he=E2=80=99s got a lot of eggs in one baske=
t and he=E2=80=99s very intelligently trying to make sure that=E2=80=99s no=
t true. We saw him do this before. He partnered with Zuck on the initial Ll=
ama open sourcing and offered that via Azure. Now he=E2=80=99s got Mistral,=
 Mistral=E2=80=99s the current open source darling and leader, and I think =
just executing with incredibly impressive speed and taste, as Daniel said.

